{"tid":92436,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解寫唔到一個翻譯完美既program?","createTime":"2017-01-23T14:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T12:37:00.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52695b58f18640c40409bbd3720df032c0f1603b","tid":92436,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"google處理咩data都完美咁濟,示範哂IT既可能性,神奇性,連人工智能都玩埋,咩BIG DATA都處理哂,屈哂機,但唯獨google翻譯真係同冇用冇分別,無論打咩落去,整一段日文落去都唔知譯左咩出黎,現今既科技,都冇法寫出一個譯得完美D既演算法?"},{"pid":"025be22c5d4169e1346fe0cdfa6fce0e0f9c6b03","tid":92436,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:01:44.000Z","msg":"其實唔難<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀過文法書"},{"pid":"b4c4b3eaf887cbb921ddfe50f9fd09d5b710e544","tid":92436,"uid":78118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5bae567bd20413c92a5e91b2976266ce98632af","tid":92436,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"你今日食左飯未都有十鳩幾種譯法"},{"pid":"4cdeb302454700ed6bed6a3d9dabf794cebe4e33","tid":92436,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:27:27.000Z","msg":"Google 個 translation 其實已經好勁<br />\n<br />\n而且佢係一路進化緊同學習緊"},{"pid":"cd4e7e7ae42796c927fe5227ab459b9569b174b1","tid":92436,"uid":78118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1066cac38c66a004e36b7cd9564b78ea4da392e9","tid":92436,"uid":12287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為語言唔係好似數學加減法<br />\n電腦程式背後係數理原理<br />\n語言應該唔能夠用數學表達</blockquote><br />\n正解<br />\n人類語言溝通能力係生物經過幾億年進化出黎，電腦唔係咁容易做到<br />\n另一個例子係圖像分柝，人眼＋腦可以好輕易分辦3D圖片／知道一張圖入面係咩黎，就算今日對AI電腦黎講依然係一個挑戰<br />\n相反，好似數學加減／數學邏輯／捉棋都係對進化多年既生物全無優勢，電腦比較容易做得比人類叻"},{"pid":"e55b51bbd8184f5245408093686de6402f8450ec","tid":92436,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"你廣東話轉書面語有時都覺得差好遠啦<br />\n更何況另一種語言"},{"pid":"ddb19108a8a6a0ec7fd0975c9760fee696f7b55a","tid":92436,"uid":12287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Google 個 translation 其實已經好勁<br />\n<br />\n而且佢係一路進化緊同學習緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最近google用machine learning，已經令google translate勁左好多<br />\n例如有啲句子佢本身只係識中譯英，識英譯法，但不試過中譯法，依加透過新系統可以譯到<br />\n不過當然同完美仲有好大距離sosad<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"https://www.newscientist.com/article/2114748-google-translate-ai-invents-its-own-language-to-translate-with/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newscientist.com%2Farticle%2F2114748-google-translate-ai-invents-its-own-language-to-translate-with%2F&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28Lvgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=138b45da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newscientist.com/article/2114748-google-translate-ai-invents-its-own-language-to-translate-with/</a>"},{"pid":"7bd8c288d8004ffefae76e21875ff49c5dbfc1da","tid":92436,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:41:18.000Z","msg":"無絕對標準<br />\n翻譯係文學嚟<br />\n好似藝術作品音樂演奏<br />\n所謂大師都係得個名"},{"pid":"e637d0026e1244fd2cd36b11289542d097ae2757","tid":92436,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"話言入面的文化係不停轉變緊<br />\n每個語言的文化又冇logic可言"},{"pid":"5495d962a120676fc04d31071388476621fe9793","tid":92436,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"「可能性、神奇性」明明係唔啱漢語嘅文法，但我地都明，咪就係語言特別之處，明明係語病都可以因為普及而變得冇問題<br />\n運算就只係可以顯示現有嘅資料，佢春知「神奇性」都有人夠膽拎出嚟用咩<br />\n你話我講得有冇道理性？"},{"pid":"a1a759b441a1eebff37dec2233dd872f00e0cca2","tid":92436,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:54:06.000Z","msg":"其實係做到<br />\n<br />\n但想樓主自己做功課"},{"pid":"d2f3d405f70ceb33bd233cd6e62df4f0eec41bc7","tid":92436,"uid":16647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T20:14:36.000Z","msg":"其實對於一個完全陌生既語言，一句裡面淨係翻譯到一兩個關鍵字眼已經有好大幫助。"},{"pid":"3a40fd998931f857bf5a2dbb7448221f8de0c00e","tid":92436,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T20:22:52.000Z","msg":"可能係deep learn終極任務"},{"pid":"bf5c1bfb240fd5b3a0bc6fc9b05f5419578005a2","tid":92436,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T20:25:17.000Z","msg":"如果係人工智能應該做到完美翻譯？"},{"pid":"483651b12172649ea6dabcde4fd2afc8a24c2435","tid":92436,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T20:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「可能性、神奇性」明明係唔啱漢語嘅文法，但我地都明，咪就係語言特別之處，明明係語病都可以因為普及而變得冇問題<br />\n運算就只係可以顯示現有嘅資料，佢春知「神奇性」都有人夠膽拎出嚟用咩<br />\n你話我講得有冇道理性？</blockquote><br />\n連樓主都未學識中文<br />\ngoogle 唔識好正常姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d63208eb8f19d064b22aabd777d5099c448f50","tid":92436,"uid":12432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T20:39:05.000Z","msg":"Google 翻譯其實一路進化緊，因為佢係用big data學習，詳細可以睇下呢篇文：<a href=\"https://www.infoworld.com/article/2612066/cloud-computing/google-taps-big-data-for-universal-translator.amp.html?client=safari\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infoworld.com%2Farticle%2F2612066%2Fcloud-computing%2Fgoogle-taps-big-data-for-universal-translator.amp.html%3Fclient%3Dsafari&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28Lvgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=ed7ba0ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.infoworld.com/article/2612066/cloud-computing/google-taps-big-data-for-universal-translator.amp.html?client=safari</a><br />\n另外，技術性翻譯例如商業翻譯、法律翻譯的確有可能俾電腦取代，但文學翻譯一定唔得。文學翻譯或多或少都包含咗譯者嘅詮釋同「再創造」，唔係純粹字對字word-for-word或者語意上semantic嘅翻譯咁簡單同直接。"},{"pid":"fd6176e6377149d39f6eb2fad68e178fb2ab36d5","tid":92436,"uid":12432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T20:41:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Google 翻譯其實一路進化緊，因為佢係用big data學習，詳細可以睇下呢篇文：<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/www.infoworld.com/article/2612066/cloud-computing/google-taps-big-data-for-universal-translator.amp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fwww.infoworld.com%2Farticle%2F2612066%2Fcloud-computing%2Fgoogle-taps-big-data-for-universal-translator.amp.html&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28Lvgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=81d177ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/www.infoworld.com/article/2612066/cloud-computing/google-taps-big-data-for-universal-translator.amp.html</a><br />\n另外，技術性翻譯例如商業翻譯、法律翻譯的確有可能俾電腦取代，但文學翻譯一定唔得。文學翻譯或多或少都包含咗譯者嘅詮釋同「再創造」，唔係純粹字對字word-for-word或者語意上semantic嘅翻譯咁簡單同直接。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e07861cdb6b6ec2d9c6be9c2dbe55c858c8f0a54","tid":92436,"uid":71266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T20:44:31.000Z","msg":"Google世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878dcd2c39bc6b1b710c26edde1d792a3001c189","tid":92436,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:00:29.000Z","msg":"你google 下nature language processing 同machine translate,就知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8547b49ba38538a86f497caa5b22834bf614fec","tid":92436,"uid":75537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:43:19.000Z","msg":"當語言翻譯同創造都俾佢掌握埋<br />\n人類被AI統治嘅時代又近左一步"},{"pid":"2d0d4df82cb7b20b3183a4e8ce0ddf36eec95d0f","tid":92436,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"因為語言影響世界觀<br />\nSapir-Whorf Hypothesis <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8089f71d4629501633756078b15937dc9c7b7ca9","tid":92436,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T08:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「可能性、神奇性」明明係唔啱漢語嘅文法，但我地都明，咪就係語言特別之處，明明係語病都可以因為普及而變得冇問題<br />\n運算就只係可以顯示現有嘅資料，佢春知「神奇性」都有人夠膽拎出嚟用咩<br />\n你話我講得有冇道理性？</blockquote><br />\n連樓主都未學識中文<br />\ngoogle 唔識好正常姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有樣野叫fuzzy logic"},{"pid":"b297fb6cf1b7d9aa5ce8275d88175d02c4ce9c84","tid":92436,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Google 翻譯其實一路進化緊，因為佢係用big data學習，詳細可以睇下呢篇文：<a href=\"https://www.infoworld.com/article/2612066/cloud-computing/google-taps-big-data-for-universal-translator.amp.html?client=safari\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infoworld.com%2Farticle%2F2612066%2Fcloud-computing%2Fgoogle-taps-big-data-for-universal-translator.amp.html%3Fclient%3Dsafari&d=SjzH5d%2B%2FsKn5MNMwa28Lvgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=ed7ba0ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.infoworld.com/article/2612066/cloud-computing/google-taps-big-data-for-universal-translator.amp.html?client=safari</a><br />\n另外，技術性翻譯例如商業翻譯、法律翻譯的確有可能俾電腦取代，但文學翻譯一定唔得。文學翻譯或多或少都包含咗譯者嘅詮釋同「再創造」，唔係純粹字對字word-for-word或者語意上semantic嘅翻譯咁簡單同直接。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係同alphago一樣自我學習中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}